     <h2><i>Body Mortgage</i> is back</h2>
<p>
A newly revised edition of my dystopian detective thriller <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Body-Mortgage-Richard-Engling/dp/0977661067/ref=tmm_pap_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&qid=1540415443&sr=8-2" target="new" ><i>Body Mortgage</i></a> is now available. It was originally published by Penguin Books USA under the Onyx imprint and by Headline House in the UK. Available in Kindle or paperback.</p>
<br>
   <h2><i>Visions of Anna</i> continues to win fans!</h2>
    <p>Chicago's <i>NewCity Lit</i> called  <i>Visions of Anna</i> "transcendent...charmed" <a href="novelist.html"><font color="#ffdead">Find out more!</font></a> Or get a copy right now at <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Visions-Anna-Richard-Engling/dp/0977661024/ref=tmm_pap_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&qid=1530300763&sr=8-1" target="new">Amazon.com</a>.</p>
<br>

